data.description: Move right in to this beautiful home that has been completely updated but retains all of the charm! Recent updates include kitchen, bathroom, metal roof, siding, windows with a transferable lifetime warranty, tankless water heater, Pex plumbing, furnace, appliances, flooring, the list goes on! There is nothing left to do but move in and decorate to make it your own. There is plenty of space outdoors in the open yard with a generous patio for bonfires on clear summer nights. This is an ideal location with a small town feel and an easy commute to Cedar Rapids and other surrounding larger towns. Make your appointment to tour it today!
